{"tid":1597801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奪命瞬間！玩滑翔傘一半…女三寶「空中尖叫」撞擊　2男墜落1死1傷","createTime":"2019-09-27T06:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T07:01:48.000Z","uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"781fb70b202fa8289925ad49c4748663bd0494b1","tid":1597801,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:14:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8wTqKctjfUE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8wTqKctjfUE&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYgWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=0133f201\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8wTqKctjfUE</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯卡巴爾達-巴爾卡爾共和國傳出滑翔傘死亡意外，2名俄羅斯男子參加飛行傘活動時，遭女玩家「空中撞擊」，當場慘叫一聲墜落，最後造成1死1傷。不少網友都認為女子應該為這場死亡意外負責，「有時間尖叫，怎麼不趕快改變方向」。<br />\n<br />\n這段滑翔傘意外影片近日在網上轉傳，畫面中只見1名男飛行員與1名男子一起穿好裝備後，開始玩飛行傘，一邊自拍，一邊俯視壯觀美景。過程中也可以看到空中還有許多滑翔傘在穿梭。<br />\n<br />\n影片最後只見一名女玩家突然從遠處開始「放聲尖叫」，並迎面擦撞。飛行員雖然大聲阻止已來不及，最後聽到一聲慘叫，及高空墜落樹林聲音。<br />\n<br />\n據《Romania TV》報導，其中一名男子死亡，另一人受傷。肇事女玩家則不認為自己要為此負責。許多網友紛紛留言「愚蠢的女孩」、「她慌了，剛開始大呼小叫，而不是改變方向」、「這種有任何法規可管？」"},{"pid":"08d444e990f46840bfa43652d7f96b1bb47e6198","tid":1597801,"uid":56847,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:19:22.000Z","msg":"點解死果個唔係條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8bcf4946d610208bf80c6df8433f5625d8afcf","tid":1597801,"uid":50745,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:23:10.000Z","msg":"女人揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e38cfd80d3f7bec29a0a08543dfc3a01e41e8f","tid":1597801,"uid":237555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:23:18.000Z","msg":"咁高跌落黎....r.i.p"},{"pid":"fbca2e276b53fdb105af4607890110bb1c2c74a3","tid":1597801,"uid":60321,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:30:14.000Z","msg":"同一個area咁多人一齊飛, 仲要個個唔同方法咁飛, 其實都幾危險下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c2ab55dee8e10ebbc88e4dbdcc11d637b467c0","tid":1597801,"uid":141378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:51:35.000Z","msg":"其實同揸船一樣，迎面要向右轉，右邊係山就有優先權<br />\n個女人都白痴，叫佢老尾"},{"pid":"17f344ca731498963d5203c4dae0980e12408bbe","tid":1597801,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:53:55.000Z","msg":"條女擺到明唔撚識渣"},{"pid":"8eefca355482ca8a175c98bdc94c7fa62022fd63","tid":1597801,"uid":34793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:55:10.000Z","msg":"女人揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c9c827c317dc57c179145f536856d41cc7bedf","tid":1597801,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:57:23.000Z","msg":"傻架?咁多人一齊飛"},{"pid":"38be4d3d55880abe7585c8ae108bddc2a938fdfd","tid":1597801,"uid":60563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:59:04.000Z","msg":"睇片其實幾危險<br />\n咁多人係唔同方向飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff7e1205efab9a512b93b6f45d6a3bdff14c63c","tid":1597801,"uid":57035,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:59:13.000Z","msg":"女人揸車出意外：啊～～～之後繼續畀油向前衝<br />\n男人揸車出意外：輕輕屌一聲 之後扭軑搵方法解決"},{"pid":"85bfd9f369fb486b07bf1667bc3d5f4b78219f65","tid":1597801,"uid":10503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0ff7e1205efab9a512b93b6f45d6a3bdff14c63c","tid":1597801,"uid":57035,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:59:13.000Z","msg":"女人揸車出意外：啊～～～之後繼續畀油向前衝<br />\n男人揸車出意外：輕輕屌一聲 之後扭軑搵方法解決"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:01:48.000Z","msg":"女人:雙手放開軑盤 掩眼尖叫"}]}